{"tid":533430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（求巴絲打屌醒）好似中意左一個好朋友","createTime":"2018-01-18T18:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:10:05.000Z","uid":93159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5b17d3e9eb91a55cee4d6ba8929f8d74dccb1caf","tid":533430,"uid":93159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:25:53.000Z","msg":"我上年9月同個ex分手<br />\n咁自己都有將件事從同身邊既朋友講<br />\n其中一個就係依個女仔<br />\n佢係一個TG(之前比男人hurt得太多次）<br />\n我同佢都係19歲<br />\n其實本身一識佢都對佢有少少好感<br />\n但之後有排唔太鍾意佢<br />\n之後因為同佢講左自己分手嗰件事<br />\n之後大家熟絡左<br />\n而且我哋科科既project 都幾乎係同一組<br />\n所以我本身就好依賴佢<br />\n佢係d lead住人既type 份人有d死硬<br />\n而我就係份人平時鳩鳩地 要認真時就好認真個type<br />\n而我地之前成日都鬧交 <br />\n但鬧完之後每次感情都比鬧交前好<br />\n有時候我甚至扮on9哄佢開心<br />\n（我自己都覺得自己有啲變態，鍾意俾佢鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n之前Ocamp我組爸佢組媽<br />\n佢係camp度成日借啲意就串我又盛<br />\n而我個feel就好似俾佢食住咁<br />\n完咗camp之後啲組仔女以為我地係一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我係真係鍾意佢，定係自己太寂寞呢<br />\n定係自己依賴佢到以為自己鍾意左佢呢？<br />\n我真係好亂 我知佢當我係兄弟姊妹<br />\n但其實男女之間真係有純友誼？<br />\n嚟緊暑假我會同佢同埋我地之間一個common fd 去旅行<br />\n其實我咪應該一直維持朋友關係最好，<br />\n費事冇咗個好朋友<br />\n我覺得搵一個女朋友唔難<br />\n搵一個知己真係好難<br />\n我同佢實在係太熟啦<br />\nWhat should I do?親愛嘅巴絲打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae546c6283a3b5384816f9de18415882e91e6be","tid":533430,"uid":73909,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:26:41.000Z","msg":"too long"},{"pid":"d0a62ef6b4bbed16962191b87cbf6d77f7c5ded5","tid":533430,"uid":93159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cae546c6283a3b5384816f9de18415882e91e6be","tid":533430,"uid":73909,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:26:41.000Z","msg":"too long"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"不知不覺打左咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb35d2ddc0c700da597db515aa1a7c060589870b","tid":533430,"uid":98410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:35:12.000Z","msg":"Why not try tgt?"},{"pid":"befa21e66c86fd5183ed3ee4066ea84c0839c1fb","tid":533430,"uid":93159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb35d2ddc0c700da597db515aa1a7c060589870b","tid":533430,"uid":98410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:35:12.000Z","msg":"Why not try tgt?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:37:30.000Z","msg":"驚冇左個好朋友，同埋佢而家同啲T B曖昧緊，其實自己都有少少唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e61b46cd2baab19db5f7839d3f53ae46de407e","tid":533430,"uid":82140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔好溝，真係會冇左個好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09c53433a687838ba0c6635b09d64f43bcfedf0","tid":533430,"uid":154556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔好呀巴打，返唔到轉頭，變左質㗎會。可能係一時冲動㗎喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:過來人，損手爛腳"},{"pid":"a303dd1e64ed4ce7f0c6c61bf0006891e613c73f","tid":533430,"uid":154556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09c53433a687838ba0c6635b09d64f43bcfedf0","tid":533430,"uid":154556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔好呀巴打，返唔到轉頭，變左質㗎會。可能係一時冲動㗎喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:過來人，損手爛腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:44:47.000Z","msg":"衝"},{"pid":"9675aef3d9b92fc5cffc29a1824dcf050e27a10a","tid":533430,"uid":93159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09c53433a687838ba0c6635b09d64f43bcfedf0","tid":533430,"uid":154556,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T18:44:34.000Z","msg":"唔好呀巴打，返唔到轉頭，變左質㗎會。可能係一時冲動㗎喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk